													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Shadowheart is unable to look away. The first masked figure steps in front of her and crouches down to her level.\r\n\r\nCamera holds on Shadowheart, with the rear of the figure only glimpsed from the corner of the frame.\r\n"
