												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "[PN] Shadowheart looks up from the ground, reacts to a large wolf moving slowing towards her, Wolf moves towards Shadowheart. Should feel threatening but also possible to ready and her farther approaching her, trying to protect her"
