												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Somewhere nearby, an eerie howl. Shadowheart stares, wide-eyed.\r\n\r\nThe shape of a large wolf steps out from the treeline and into the moonlight. It closes on Shadowheart, unhurried.\r\n"
												}
